{
  "chapter": 10,
  "chapter_summary": "第十回\"燕归去\"主要讲述了芮玮离开天池府后，与夏诗一同前往黑堡复仇的途中经历。芮玮在金陵安置夏诗后，独自前往黑堡，在途中遇到简怀萱和简召舞兄妹，以及刘育芷姑娘。在黑堡附近，芮玮遇到范宗宁父子，得知黑堡正在为林三寒的女儿招亲。芮玮回忆起儿时与林三寒女儿的往事，心中复杂。本章展现了芮玮的江湖历练和情感纠葛，为后续复仇埋下伏笔。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "jian huai xuan",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你不是我的大哥！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "jian huai xuan",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你不是我的大哥……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "jian zhao wu",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "妹妹，这么晚了，还去猎什么狮子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "jian huai xuan",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "大哥，你为什么不笑呢？你要笑起来像他一样，不是很好看吗？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "jian zhao wu",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "他是什么人，要我像他！不要胡说八道，快回万寿居去！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "jian huai xuan",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你……你……没有死？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "rui wei",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "当然没死，若是死了，怎能站在这里和你讲话？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "jian huai xuan",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "那我就放心了，那天你被我大哥打伤，我真怕你就此去世，亏得老天有眼，否则……",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "jian zhao wu",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "你还乱说什么？快快回去。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "rui wei",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "你已知前年是我装扮你的哥来到此地了吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "jian huai xuan",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "当然知道！你快让开，我要过去……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "rui wei",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "简兄，你曾说就是刘姑娘知道你的阴谋也不饶她，为何你的妹妹早已知道，却没有关系？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "jian zhao wu",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "本公子家事，要你多管？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "jian huai xuan",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "因为我不会将你装扮我哥哥的事告诉妈，大哥便饶了我啦！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "jian huai xuan",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你快闪开，让我过去嘛！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "rui wei",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "简兄，你既相信妹妹，为何不敢相信刘姑娘？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "jian zhao wu",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "阁下时时提到她，是何原故？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "rui wei",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "春琴、冬画是你的丫环，总该相信她们，不应杀害……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "jian huai xuan",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我哥哥无端怎会去杀春琴和冬画？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "rui wei",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "只因她们知道我曾装扮你哥哥来到此地！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "jian huai xuan",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "大哥，是真的吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "jian zhao wu",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "那两个丫头不知轻重，嘴巴会乱说，若是说与母亲知道，我叫陌生人装扮来府，岂不要惹她老人家生气，不如杀了灭口！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "rui wei",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "你敢杀了她两人，芮某永生决不饶你！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "jian zhao wu",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "本公子会怕你的恐吓，你看着我立时就要将她们杀了！",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "jian huai xuan",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "大哥我求你不要杀了她们，好吗？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "jian zhao wu",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "你快回去罢，我不杀她们就是！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "jian huai xuan",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "text": "谢谢大哥，妹妹回去了！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "rui wei",
      "listener": "char_xia_shi",
      "text": "我们走吗！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "jian huai xuan",
      "listener": "char_xia_shi",
      "text": "你要到哪里去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_shi",
      "speaker_name": "xia shi",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "我跟芮公子离开这里……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 91,
      "line_end": 91
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "jian huai xuan",
      "listener": "char_xia_shi",
      "text": "你能服侍他，很有福气……",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 93,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "rui wei",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "在下并非叫她服侍我……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 95,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "jian zhao wu",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "总有一日，我要那贱婢死在我手下……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 99,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "liu yu zhi",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "外面是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "liu yu zhi",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "可是芮相公吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "rui wei",
      "listener": "char_liu_yu_zhi",
      "text": "在下芮玮拜访刘姑娘。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "liu yu zhi",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "进来吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "rui wei",
      "listener": "char_liu_yu_zhi",
      "text": "多谢姑娘今日救命之恩。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "liu yu zhi",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "哪用谢，我无法现身相助，用牛毛天王针刺相公，相公不要见怪。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "rui wei",
      "listener": "char_liu_yu_zhi",
      "text": "我也太差劲了，竟然会被简公子激怒，若非姑娘那三针救我，芮某早已死在公子的手下，在下感恩不尽，怎会怪姑娘。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "liu yu zhi",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "其实相公因妾身之故才被受激，我……我……怎该不救你呢……",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "rui wei",
      "listener": "char_liu_yu_zhi",
      "text": "我……我……要……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "liu yu zhi",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "相公要走了吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "liu yu zhi",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "白天我用传音入密给相公说话后，便猜测相公晚上会来道谢，现在讲过了，当然要走了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "liu yu zhi",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "相公请坐，我去拿盏茶来。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "liu yu zhi",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "相公有这般奇遇，妾身也为高兴，目下讲来简公子已非你的对手，但想明年八月中秋之约，要知残叟早岁便已闻名江湖，武功皆都高过简公子，相公赴约时可要特别谨慎。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "rui wei",
      "listener": "char_liu_yu_zhi",
      "text": "谢谢姑娘的关怀，不知姑娘住在这里可好？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "liu yu zhi",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "好与不好有何分别，命已前定，改也改不掉了！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "liu yu zhi",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "恨不相逢未嫁时……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "rui wei",
      "listener": "char_liu_yu_zhi",
      "text": "姑……姑娘……我要走了……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "liu yu zhi",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我送相公至门口！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "liu yu zhi",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "相公如今到何方去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "rui wei",
      "listener": "char_liu_yu_zhi",
      "text": "我自幼住在山西黑堡，如今要回去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "liu yu zhi",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "相公回黑堡做什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "rui wei",
      "listener": "char_liu_yu_zhi",
      "text": "黑堡有我不共戴天之仇，我要去了结！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "liu yu zhi",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "相公一路平安，望早日得报父仇……",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "rui wei",
      "listener": "char_liu_yu_zhi",
      "text": "多谢姑娘，后会有期！",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_shi",
      "speaker_name": "xia shi",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "相公去黑堡复仇，带着妾身颇为不便，不如将妾留在此地如何？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_zong_ning",
      "speaker_name": "fan zong ning",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "简公子！简公子！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_zong_ning",
      "speaker_name": "fan zong ning",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "简公子还认识在下吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "rui wei",
      "listener": "char_fan_zong_ning",
      "text": "兄台是……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_zong_ning",
      "speaker_name": "fan zong ning",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "公子贵人，尚记得淮西范宗宁否？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "rui wei",
      "listener": "char_fan_zong_ning",
      "text": "原来是范兄？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_zong_ning",
      "speaker_name": "fan zong ning",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "范某仅在淮西与公子一面，想不到公子还未忘记。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "rui wei",
      "listener": "char_fan_zong_ning",
      "text": "范兄远离淮西来此，有何贵干？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_zong_ning",
      "speaker_name": "fan zong ning",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "还不是为了小儿的婚事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_zong_ning",
      "speaker_name": "fan zong ning",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "还记得犬子范大康吗？他那日蒙公子教导，迄今还常说受益匪浅，能不能与公子长聚一些时日……",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_da_kang",
      "speaker_name": "fan da kang",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "简公子！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "rui wei",
      "listener": "char_fan_da_kang",
      "text": "大康兄春风满面，定有喜事。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_da_kang",
      "speaker_name": "fan da kang",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "有何喜事？能再见简公子一面便是最大的喜事了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "rui wei",
      "listener": "char_fan_da_kang",
      "text": "令尊适才说为了你的婚事来此，怎说没有喜事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_da_kang",
      "speaker_name": "fan da kang",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "那还不知成不成，若说是喜事未免太早！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_zong_ning",
      "speaker_name": "fan zong ning",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "小儿技艺浅薄，来此不过碰碰运气罢了！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "rui wei",
      "listener": "char_fan_zong_ning",
      "text": "婚事是否有困难，是否要小弟效力之处？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_zong_ning",
      "speaker_name": "fan zong ning",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "多谢为小儿挂心，但是这件事除了他自己外，别人是帮不了忙的！",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "rui wei",
      "listener": "char_fan_zong_ning",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_zong_ning",
      "speaker_name": "fan zong ning",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "公子有否发觉太原突然多了不少携礼的武林人物？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "rui wei",
      "listener": "char_fan_zong_ning",
      "text": "我见着六批向城西走去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_zong_ning",
      "speaker_name": "fan zong ning",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "他们都是到黑堡求婚去的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "rui wei",
      "listener": "char_fan_zong_ning",
      "text": "求婚？求什么婚？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_zong_ning",
      "speaker_name": "fan zong ning",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "敢情公子还不知武林中最近有件热闹的消息吧？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "rui wei",
      "listener": "char_fan_zong_ning",
      "text": "什么消息？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_zong_ning",
      "speaker_name": "fan zong ning",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "此地非谈话之所，我们到茶馆坐坐。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_zong_ning",
      "speaker_name": "fan zong ning",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "黑堡堡主林三寒有个武功容貌皆佳的掌上明珠，公子可知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "rui wei",
      "listener": "char_fan_zong_ning",
      "text": "知道！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_zong_ning",
      "speaker_name": "fan zong ning",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "上月林三寒突然向武林宣布，要替自己的女儿招一位乘龙快婿，希望武林中的少侠多多应征……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_zong_ning",
      "speaker_name": "fan zong ning",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "林三寒怕武林中的后彦不来应征，另外附道：凡被招中的女婿，亲传生平绝技一种，并赠避毒珠一颗，黄金百镒！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "rui wei",
      "listener": "char_fan_zong_ning",
      "text": "是故范兄也带令郎来应征了……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_zong_ning",
      "speaker_name": "fan zong ning",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "范某倒看不上那颗避毒珠与黄金，实是传闻林三寒的女儿貌美贤淑之故，犬子年龄已大，当该替他选个佳偶。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_zong_ning",
      "speaker_name": "fan zong ning",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "江湖闻讯赶来少年俊彦，不知凡几，今日便是选拔之日，林三寒要选出武功最高，像貌最好的少侠为婿。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_da_kang",
      "speaker_name": "fan da kang",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大康自觉武功低弱，要想选上实非易事。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_zong_ning",
      "speaker_name": "fan zong ning",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "如今有幸碰到简公子，能指教犬子一二，犬子选中的希望就大多了！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_da_kang",
      "speaker_name": "fan da kang",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "公子技艺超群，那年一夕谈话，大康才知武道之深，今日若能再得一二指教，实乃三生之幸！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "rui wei",
      "listener": "char_fan_da_kang",
      "text": "近日身体不舒，他日再与大康兄聚谈。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_zong_ning",
      "speaker_name": "fan zong ning",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "多有打扰简公子，范某与犬子就住在黑堡，公子请继续用茶。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_han",
      "speaker_name": "gao han",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "喂！你是黑堡里的兄弟吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "rui wei",
      "listener": "char_gao_han",
      "text": "兄弟不是黑堡里的人，你要找谁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    }
